      <para>
        The first step is to configure yum to enable the Ulteo rpm repository.
        Create the file <emphasis>/etc/yum.repos.d/ovd.repo</emphasis> with:</para>
       <screen>
<![CDATA[[ovd-@VERSIONNOTILD@]
name=Ulteo OVD @VERSION@
baseurl=@BASE_URI@/rhel/@distrib_version@/
enabled=1
gpgcheck=1
gpgkey=@BASE_URI@/rhel/@distrib_version@/keyring]]>
        </screen>
    </section>

